<p>We are located at Lanzhou University, a beautiful city which passed through by Yellow River (see e.g. <a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%B0%E5%B7%9E%E5%B8%82">Wikipedia: Lanzhou City</a>). We exchange ideas and work with our neighbors from <a href="http://iie.lzu.edu.cn/lzupage/B20180912024139.html">Institute of Innovation Ecology</a>, as well as with the colleagues from University of Haifa, Havard University and etc.</p>

